sentences: Erika Radermacher (born 16 April 1936) is a German pianist, soprano and composer.
After 1970 she became more interested in composition.
Two prizes, BAT competition for new chamber music, 1982
Music Prize of the Canton of Bern, 1983 (with Schneider)
First Prize in the Summer Academy in Salzburg
Robert Walser in der Schweizer Musik (Musiques Suisses Nr. 6231, 2005)
Historic Recordings 1968-1998, New Horizons Ensemble (music scene in Switzerland - Grammont Portrait
Urs Peter Schneider (Edition Wandelweiser Records No. 101, 2001) Artists: Schneider, Urs Peter; Rader, Erika
No. 012 / UTR4132, 2000) Artists: Rader, Erika; Weber, Katharina
